default10default&#xa0; 
defaultA range of studies
default 
defaultdemonstrates that effective ways to reach older women and men who are 
defaultdisabled and living in poverty is by ensuring income security through social protection and livelihoods support. This needs to be combined with effective, appropriate, safe and affordable healthcare, backed up by robust information services, citizen guaran
defaulttees and a reliable complaints system to ensure entitlements are upheld.
